以拎野抵抗，陣間就會兩個都拉</blockquote><br />\n所以你話練跑係幾咁緊要</blockquote><br />\n根本呢D法例不合時宜<br />\n點解反抗係犯法<br />\n逃跑先係合理?<br />\n人地美國俾人打劫一鳩野開槍啪落去啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講咁多不如練下跑步，陣間街上有精神病人亂斬你，你都有得走</blockquote><br />\n你話香港人幾撚可恥，係自己地方受攻擊竟然只可以逃走，難怪香港人打都無打過就日日講移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aeca5da5aa5141ac2c5c12cfb7d60fd89fc836e","tid":235640,"uid":112615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T22:36:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港法律萬歲，總之你犯法就係你唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係要你唔識反抗呀，遲D再教埋你要接受"},{"pid":"3a5613a728fd12de9ee938373b6fa5f013d2af96","tid":235640,"uid":58669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T23:00:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明顯呢條例係比法官同警察少d野做<br />\n<br />\n唔駛查邊個打邊個先，兩個都拉晒</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/gamefp_213650515858d4f87786bb2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2Fgamefp_213650515858d4f87786bb2.png&h=445775cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0822127b9926cccffa79ba5e9281d404e0074b7","tid":235640,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T23:10:16.000Z","msg":"你不如認識下咩叫自衛殺人"},{"pid":"3f3fff664cb86d1b8be58294fc4dd995dc6d27f0","tid":235640,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T23:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你不如認識下咩叫自衛殺人</blockquote><br />\n212 侵害人身罪 8"},{"pid":"331ee99407636a55c3e3c013d99b10535241a146","tid":235640,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T23:14:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你不如認識下咩叫自衛殺人</blockquote><br />\n212 侵害人身罪 8</blockquote><br />\non9仔，女仔體力都弱d又失左先機，無高一級武功根本死硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d93e49dd14e81ffdaa07701a10b824c706c35e5","tid":23